{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Nationwide vote to decide London's mayor",
        "additional_details": "This is because London is the capital city and we feel it should be the country that votes for the mayor of its capital city.\r\n",
        "background": "London is the capital city of our great nation, we believe there should be a nationwide vote for who runs it, as what happens in London, has a knock on effect for the rest of the country.",
